            </div>
            <div style="display: flex;flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
                <h3 style="margin: 0;color: #124f89;">Office Address :</h3>
                <p style="margin: 0;opacity: 0.7;">Office No. 915, "The Summit Business Bay", <br>
                    Behind Guru Nanak Petrol Pump, Off. Andheri-Kurla Road, <br>
                    Andheri (East), Mumbai 400 069</p>
            </div>
        </div>
            <div style="">
                <h3 style="margin: 0;color: #124f89;text-align: right;">INDEX</h3>
                <p style="text-align: right;opacity: 0.7;">Global Summary</p>
